The Mass Key shipyards, started out as a single kerbal's dream of making it to the stars. And not long afterwards they were sending up Kerban shaking rockets with kerbalnuats aboard. The Mass Key shipyards currently have 3 factories to make there crafts, and at lest 2 rocket launch sites. The Mass Key shipyards Can accept other kerbals designs to launch into space, provided that we carry the parts for the design.
